short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: Access your Topicus KeyHub vaults directly from your browser.
short.de: Zugriff auf Ihren Topicus KeyHub Safes direkt aus Ihrem Browser.
short.nl: Benader je Topicus KeyHub-kluizen direct vanuit je browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Topicus KeyHub lifts Identity & Access Management to the next level with a new revolutionary security structure: central authentication and decentral autorisation.

All your corporate passwords are securely stored in Topicus KeyHub and with this browser extension they are right there when you need them.

Thanks to the decentralized autorisation structure, you only have access to the corporate passwords you need. Based on the groups you have access to you will find all passwords right here.

IMPORTANT: This extension requires a Topicus KeyHub license. For more information visit www.topicus-keyhub.com
